July 29, 2017 4:43 AM ET
Food Products

Company Overview of Zest Tea, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Zest Tea, LLC produces tea. The company offers various tea varieties, including apple cinnamon black tea, black citrus tea, earl grey black tea, and pomegranate mojito green tea. Its products are available through small shops. The company serves customers in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania; and Stonington, Connecticut. Zest Tea, LLC was founded in 2014 and is based in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania.


2101 Chestnut StreetSuite 324Philadelphia, PA 19103United StatesFounded in 2014



Phone: 215-567-3835

www.getzesttea.com







