Zest High Caffeine Teas

















Amino Acids


Natural Caffeine


Steady Alertness




L-Theanine is a rare amino acid found in Zest Tea that helps increase cognitive function, enhance mood, and improve memory. 


Zest Tea's all-natural caffeine increases energy, alertness, and stamina. Caffeine has also been shown to ward off a variety of diseases.


The L-Theanine and Caffeine in Zest Tea fuse for a steady and prolonged alertness, without the jitters & crash.






 
Zest Tea is a line of high caffeine energy boosting teas. Zest’s premium tea blends have comparable caffeine levels to coffee, for an energizing kick, and amino acids shown reduce the jitters and crash while boosting cognitive functions. The result is a steady and prolonged alertness.
 




Zest Tea Caffeine Levels




Zest Black Tea



155mg / cup


Zest tea has as much caffeine as a cup of coffee, or about 3x the levels of normal teas. We use a proprietary blending process and natural caffeine extract to enhance the caffeine levels of our teas. This makes Zest the tea with the highest caffeine on the market!
Our biggest concern when developing these teas was maintaining the delicious flavor profiles of our base teas. If you look at our reviews you'll see that we accomplished this task. Our teas are applauded as much for their premium flavors as they are the enhanced energy levels!




Zest Green Tea



135 mg / cup




Coffee



125 mg / cup




Traditional Black Tea



50 mg / cup




Traditional Green Tea



25 mg / cup




 
"We felt 'in the zone' almost more clearheaded than we would normally be with coffee... It definitely hits you harder, but I didn't get jittery or anything"
- Philly.com 
 




Focused Energy




The combination of the caffeine and L-Theanine (a rare amino acid) in Zest Tea has a synergistic effect that prolongs the energy levels and creates a more steady alertness. A side effect of the energy moderation is a reduction in the "jitters" and "crash" that typically accompanies caffeinated beverages.  





  





"Tastes great and good energy. Have literally stopped drinking coffee since getting my first batch of zest tea!!"
Billy Schrero





"Perks me up 10x better than coffee, amazing!" 
Daniel Rodic





"I know the selling point of Zest Teas are the caffeine, but honestly the flavor is what keeps me coming back. I have never had such a flavorful tea that was not overpowering. This stuff is awesome."
 Nick Loadholtes


"I love coffee but from having my first cup of Zest Tea all I can say is WOW."
Daniel Becker




 




 Blue Lady Black Tea


Pomegranate Mojito Green Tea


Earl Grey Black Tea


Apple Cinnamon Black Tea










South Indian black tea with an aromatic mix of orange, lemon, hibiscus and a peppering of vivid blue cornflower petals


Young hyson green tea with a refreshingly aromatic blend of peppermint, lime, and pomegranate


Premium Nilgiri Indian black tea blended with a delicious bergamot essential oil


Orange Pekoe black tea smothered in real bits of apple and cinnamon










