Zest Tea, LLC


        Winner of Best New Product at the 2015 World Tea Expo, Zest brings innovation to an industry steeped in tradition. Most new developments in the tea industry have related to the tea bags, but Zest brings new and exciting features to the tea itself with their high caffeine blends. Furthermore, half of our customers identify as tea drinkers and the other half as former coffee drinkers. Zest is pulling new customers into the tea market.
    

From the 63rd Summer Fancy Food Show 2017
                 (booth 5119)
            

Winner of the Best New Product at the 2015 World Tea Expo, Zest premium energy teas offer the same energizing kick of coffee without the negative side effects. Despite our teas having comparable caffeine levels to coffee—about three times the levels of traditional teas—the amino acids in Zest help create a steady and prolonged alertness, instead of the jitters and crash associated with other caffeinated products.



