With the Argo Tea App:

Enjoy a $2 credit on us just for downloading!
Earn TEAriffic rewards as you progress through 4 status levels
Get $4 credit for every 10 visits ($5 at CelebriTEA & RoyalTEA status)
Order ahead and prepay right from your phone
Seamlessly scan to pay at the counter
Migrate the value of your current drink points, accumulated rewards and stored value over to the new program
Share Argo love with your friends. Send them a $2 credit and when they spend it, you’ll also earn $2
Gift Cards – Easily send Argo Tea e-gift cards to your friends




Download the App Now!


Questions?
If you have questions about the app, please visit our FAQs. You can also email us or contact Customer Support from within the app for additional assistance.




