Cinnamon Apple Black










              
                 
                  $12.75 
                
              
            


          
            $14.75
          
         





Notify me when this product is available:
















TYPE (TIN, POUCH, LOOSE LEAF):

Tin (16 Sachets)
Pouch (20 Sachets)
Loose Leaf (2 oz | ~25 servings | 33% savings)
Loose Leaf (4 oz | ~50 servings | 36% savings)
Loose Leaf (8 oz | ~100 servings | 37% savings)
Loose Leaf (16 oz | ~200 servings | 41% savings)



Quantity:



Add to Cart



 Free Shipping On Orders Over $40
 Loose Leaf Special: Save over 40% per serving buying loose leaf! Brew loose leaf teas with ease using our discounted filter packs & infusers!






Collections:

Original Blends, 
              
                Premium Caffeinated Tea Blends, 
              
                Zest Products



Type: Black Tea









We looked to American icons when creating this blend and what’s more American than Apple Pie? Unfortunately, football and the Grand Canyon didn’t make for great teas. This blend of premium Orange Pekoe black tea smothered in real bits of apple and cinnamon is a nod to your grandmother’s 4th of July specialty.
 




Tea Base: Flower Orange Pekoe
Base Region: South India
Ingredients: South Indian Flower Orange Pekoe Black Tea, Cinnamon Chips, Apple Pieces, Cinnamon Flavor, Apple Flavor, Natural Caffeine
16 pyramid bags per tin and 20 pyramid bags per refill!
Caffeine: Approximately 150 mg/ cup - About the same as a cup of coffee!
 




Want to save some money?
Create a discounted auto-delivery plan!
Save over 30% and free shipping!
You choose what flavors you want and how often you want them shipped.










